issue.title: (#1430) MkHook.json

repository.name: jcabi-github
repository.description: Java Object-Oriented Wrapper of GitHub API, with a fake implementation of the entire GitHub API (for your tests)

issue.body:
This PR is for #1430:
* Implemented `MkHook.json()`
* Enabled some tests
* Left puzzle for adding more tests + fixing `MkHooks.create()`

The mock hook's data will be stored as an XML that mirrors [github's json structure](https://developer.github.com/v3/repos/hooks/#get-single-hook).
